[SN]TITLE[SN]
Tributes to 'devoted mum' found dead after fire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Tributes have been paid to a "devoted mum" found dead after a house fire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The body of Andraya Lyons, 39, was found in Drew Street, Swindon at 05:40 GMT on Saturday.
Anthony Porter, 32, has appeared before Swindon Magistrates' Court charged with murder.
Her family said: "We are completely devastated to have lost Andraya... The past few days have been really difficult for us as a family."
"She was a devoted mum to her boys and very much loved by all who knew her," they said.  Adding: "We will always treasure the memories we have of Andraya."
Mr Porter, also from Swindon, has been remanded in custody and will appear before Bristol Crown Court on Wednesday.
